title: ESET Endpoint Security v5.0.2237
description:
Changelog
Version 5.0.2237.0
Fixed: IDS settings are not applied when installing .exe package installer created in ESET Remote Administrator using Remote Desktop Protocol (RDP).
Fixed: Potentially Unwanted Application setting not overtaken after installation from prepared config xml file in the same folder as .msi installer.
Fixed: Several text inconsistencies in various languages.
